        "# Include and execute your code here\n",
        "\n",
        "# The code below uses some basic SQL code to read in the entire 'batting' table in the database and store it in a polars dataframe called 'results'. You must write polars code to manipulate the results dataframe to address the task.\n",
        "\n",
        "q = \"\"\"\n",
